    <item>
      <title>印尼印度人对特朗普关税的担忧跌至五年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/indonesian-rupiah-falls-to-five-year-low-on-trump-tariff-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼卢比（Indonesian Rupiah）在近五年内跌至其最低水平，因为对美国关税的担忧减轻了风险情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/indonesian-rupiah-falls-to-five-year-low-on-trump-tariff-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 02:07:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对能源目标的滑倒使气候目标处于危险之中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/china-s-slippage-on-energy-targets-puts-climate-goals-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在近二十年的时间里，中国通过监视其消耗的能量来实现增长的能量来对经济进行评分。将于今年结束;远远没有官方目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/china-s-slippage-on-energy-targets-puts-climate-goals-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 02:05:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对习近平施加压力，最新威胁要提高关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-piles-pressure-on-xi-with-latest-threat-to-raise-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统宣布了对中国进口的额外关税，这增加了北京加大报复的风险，并在世界两个最大的经济体之间施加了紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-piles-pressure-on-xi-with-latest-threat-to-raise-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 02:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着加密抛售加深，比特币从历史高25％下降了25％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/bitcoin-down-25-from-all-time-high-as-crypto-selloff-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五在亚洲交易时间内，比特币的溃败恶化了，与六周前的历史最高水平下降了25％，因为交易者反向美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）当选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/bitcoin-down-25-from-all-time-high-as-crypto-selloff-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:42:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普所说，中国股票下跌，我们将征收更多的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/chinese-stocks-fall-as-trump-says-us-will-impose-more-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他将对亚洲国家的进口征收额外的10％税，这一发展增加了投资者对加剧贸易紧张局势的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/chinese-stocks-fall-as-trump-says-us-will-impose-more-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:41:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的最新关税震动有市场警报中国的回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-s-latest-tariff-jolt-has-markets-alert-for-china-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最新的关税威胁促使投资者淘汰中国的反应，而诸如新鲜刺激和宽松的货币政策之类的举动被认为是桌面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/trump-s-latest-tariff-jolt-has-markets-alert-for-china-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:39:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲芯片在NVIDIA收入上分享了跌倒，关税担心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/asian-chip-shares-drop-after-nvidia-tumbles-on-earnings-outlook-m7o3c4k4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[NVIDIA的收入和额外的美国关税的幽灵降低了亚洲芯片股票的差异，使日本高科技的Nikkei平均水平降低到9月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/asian-chip-shares-drop-after-nvidia-tumbles-on-earnings-outlook-m7o3c4k4</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:24:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通过谈论“供应改革2.0”抓住的中国钢铁部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/ailing-china-steel-sector-seized-by-talk-of-supply-reform-2-0</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国十亿吨的钢铁行业正朝着十年来最大的改动方面发展，据推测北京将订购工厂关闭，以响应在家中的建筑放缓和海外贸易保护主义浪潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-28/ailing-china-steel-sector-seized-by-talk-of-supply-reform-2-0</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 01:15:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
